Lebel Says Canada to Build Bridge Over St. Lawrence in Montreal

-- B y   T h e o p h i l o s   A r g i t i s
-- 
2011-10-05T16:14:19Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-05/lebel-says-canada-to-build-bridge-over-st-lawrence-in-montreal.html
Canadian Transport Minister Denis
Lebel said his government plans to build a new bridge across the
St. Lawrence river in  Montreal , starting with studies and
discussions with regional mayors and the Quebec provincial
government.  Lebel, in a statement posted on his website, said the
government will look at a partnership with private companies, as
well as tolls to finance construction.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Theophilos Argitis in Ottawa at 
 targitis@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Paul Badertscher at 
 pbadertscher@bloomberg.net  